parts.text: I will generate a modern minimalist illustration with a vertical 3:4 aspect ratio depicting the aesthetic of logical problem-solving. The image will feature two interconnected puzzle pieces, perfectly fitted together, symbolizing a solution. Alternatively, it might show two distinct thought bubbles seamlessly merging into a single, unified thought bubble, representing collaborative thinking leading to a common understanding. The color palette will be clean and structured, utilizing muted shades of blues and greens to create a clinical yet warm ambiance. The overall style will emphasize architectural precision, evoking structured thinking and finding common ground through collaboration.
